# HerbstPhoto v4 for Flux 2

> Analog film aesthetic LoRA. Trained on original photography. Ethically sourced.

[![Download on Patreon](https://img.shields.io/badge/Download-Patreon-FF424D?style=flat-square&logo=patreon)](https://www.patreon.com/posts/herbstphoto-v4-2-145298480)

---

## Overview

HerbstPhoto_v4_Flux2 is a LoRA model that introduces authentic analog film characteristics to Flux 2 Dev outputs. Trained exclusively on analog photography I own the rights to—no scraped data, no unlicensed material.

**What it does:**
- Filmic softness and natural grain behavior across exposure levels
- Emulsion bloom & halation
- Optical artifacts: lens flares, light leaks, chromatic aberration, barrel distortion
- Aggressive low-latitude contrast: clipped highlights, crushed shadows

The result: images that feel shot, not generated.

