## Training Details

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| Base Model | Flux 2 Dev (Black Forest Labs) |
| Framework | AI Toolkit (Ostris, LLC) |
| Hardware | H200 GPU cluster (Runpod) |
| Training Runs | 100+ |
| Methodology | Single parameter changes per run for clean A/B testing |
| Dataset | Original analog photography (full rights ownership) |

---

## Ethical Training

This model is trained **exclusively** on photographs I created and own. 

I believe we can take control of AI's potential by training on our own material—and that we can build accessible tools that empower individuals, not just corporations.


